{"word":"G4087 - πικραίνω - pikraínō - pik-rah'-ee-no - Be bitter","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πικραίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pikraínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pik-rah'-ee-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be bitter"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கசப்பாயிரு, கசந்துகொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to make bitter"},{"paragraph":"2. to embitter, to exasperate, to render angry, indignant"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4089 - πικρός - pikrós - pik-ros'/4089\">G4089</a>; to <i>embitter</i> (literally or figuratively): - be (make) bitter."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3893 - παραπικραίνω - parapikraínō - par-ap-ik-rah'-ee-no/3893\">G3893</a>, <a href=\"#/G3894 - παραπικρασμός - parapikrasmós - par-ap-ik-ras-mos'/3894\">G3894</a>, <a href=\"#/G4087 - πικραίνω - pikraínō - pik-rah'-ee-no/4087\">G4087</a>, <a href=\"#/G4088 - πικρία - pikría - pik-ree'-ah/4088\">G4088</a>, <a href=\"#/G4089 - πικρός - pikrós - pik-ros'/4089\">G4089</a>, <a href=\"#/G4090 - πικρῶς - pikrōs - pik-roce'/4090\">G4090</a>"}]}